1
00:00:40,790 --> 00:00:43,250
Do you want to go to the place
in the painting?

2
00:00:43,390 --> 00:00:45,110
But I don't know where it is.

3
00:00:45,590 --> 00:00:45,710
[Celebrating the 15th Anniversary
Sharing Love with Millions of Readers]

4
00:00:45,710 --> 00:00:47,600
I haven't even seen real snow yet.

5
00:00:48,710 --> 00:00:51,000
We'll go together when we grow up.

6
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:52,520
We'll definitely find it.

7
00:00:54,430 --> 00:00:57,030
Then we'll build a house there,

8
00:00:57,030 --> 00:00:58,450
and be together forever.

9
00:00:59,350 --> 00:01:00,430
It's a deal then.

10
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:01,280
Pinky swear.

11
00:02:31,590 --> 00:02:35,910
[THE GUILTY]

12
00:02:36,140 --> 00:02:40,200
[Episode 9]

13
00:02:40,630 --> 00:02:41,430
Love-sick fool?

14
00:02:41,430 --> 00:02:44,090
What have you learned
from that love-sick fool?

15
00:02:46,310 --> 00:02:48,400
You're throwing your brother
into the fire!

16
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:50,260
You gave him Ma Derong's address!

17
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,960
Do you want to get him killed?

18
00:02:56,870 --> 00:02:57,630
Uncle San,

19
00:02:59,190 --> 00:03:01,050
I asked Chang to find the address.

20
00:03:03,030 --> 00:03:03,790
Don't worry.

21
00:03:05,590 --> 00:03:07,870
I know what's going on
between Xia Xue and me.

22
00:03:07,870 --> 00:03:09,030
Even if I save her,

23
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,610
we can't leave Nanping.

24
00:03:13,470 --> 00:03:14,800
I just want to know

25
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:16,500
where she is right now.

26
00:03:16,690 --> 00:03:19,079
[Harmony Brings Prosperity]

27
00:03:19,079 --> 00:03:20,010
Love-sick fool.

28
00:03:20,510 --> 00:03:21,070
Fine.

29
00:03:22,190 --> 00:03:23,630
I'll get you some men

30
00:03:24,190 --> 00:03:25,450
to get her back for you.

31
00:03:25,870 --> 00:03:26,430
Alright?

32
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:31,829
An egg shouldn't strike a rock.

33
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:35,840
Right now, I need you to survive!

34
00:03:36,300 --> 00:03:37,850
You still owe me money!

35
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:52,140
This is the debt I just collected.

36
00:03:53,710 --> 00:03:55,370
I'm paying you back with this.

37
00:03:56,460 --> 00:03:57,990
Now I don't owe you anymore.

38
00:03:58,460 --> 00:04:01,450
[Harmony Brings Prosperity]

39
00:04:11,870 --> 00:04:12,400
Stop.

40
00:04:20,790 --> 00:04:21,670
Chang,

41
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:23,530
keep an eye on him for me.

42
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,190
Okay, Uncle San.

43
00:04:30,830 --> 00:04:31,830
Mr. Ma,

44
00:04:32,150 --> 00:04:35,360
the demolition of the houses in He Village
is almost complete.

45
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,480
Once the signing is done,

46
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:39,080
the shipyard branch
will be built on schedule.

47
00:04:42,150 --> 00:04:43,940
Whether you help me or not,

48
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:46,010
I will be grateful.

49
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:50,460
Even if I end up fighting Ma Derong alone,

50
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:52,630
I still know

51
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:55,210
that everyone hopes I will win.

52
00:04:56,500 --> 00:04:58,300
It's because if we win this time,

53
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:00,940
we can live in peace
for the rest of our lives.

54
00:05:01,310 --> 00:05:04,240
So even if there are
difficulties and dangers ahead,

55
00:05:04,870 --> 00:05:06,070
I've still decided

56
00:05:06,650 --> 00:05:07,870
to give it a shot.

57
00:05:09,820 --> 00:05:10,950
President, please.

58
00:05:11,390 --> 00:05:11,950
Please.

59
00:05:15,630 --> 00:05:16,870
The first installment from the bank

60
00:05:16,870 --> 00:05:19,870
will be released right after the signing.

61
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:24,100
He's just a kid from another village.

62
00:05:25,190 --> 00:05:27,070
Even he knows to strive for respect,

63
00:05:27,070 --> 00:05:28,270
to live a decent life.

64
00:05:28,270 --> 00:05:30,020
Men of He Village,

65
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:33,480
our ancestors
were burned to nothing by them.

66
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:35,800
Can we swallow this insult?

67
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:39,190
Since you saved me from the factory,

68
00:05:39,190 --> 00:05:40,320
I've made up my mind.

69
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:41,940
Count me in

70
00:05:42,030 --> 00:05:43,490
for taking down Ma Derong.

71
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:48,530
This time, I'm betting all my chips...

72
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:53,190
on you.

73
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:56,810
Alright! Let's do it!

74
00:06:02,540 --> 00:06:06,480
[Certificate: Regarding
Hengchuang Group's Violent Demolition]

75
00:06:08,210 --> 00:06:09,250
[Certificate: Regarding
Hengchuang Group's Violent Demolition]

76
00:06:16,830 --> 00:06:17,680
Thank you for coming to
guide our work at the shipyard.

77
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:19,170
[Three Days Countdown
for the Signing Ceremony]

78
00:06:19,170 --> 00:06:20,270
You must be tired from the journey.

79
00:06:20,270 --> 00:06:21,430
Let's have a simple meal.

80
00:06:21,430 --> 00:06:22,630
You're too kind, Ma.

81
00:06:22,630 --> 00:06:23,890
It's the least I can do.

82
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:26,630
I heard the shipyard laid off
another batch of old employees.

83
00:06:26,630 --> 00:06:28,480
It's unavoidable
during the transformation.

84
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:29,410
Watch your step.

85
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:31,120
The shipyard explosion earlier

86
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,270
put the provincial government
in a tough spot.

87
00:06:32,270 --> 00:06:34,200
Some people used it to make a scene.

88
00:06:34,950 --> 00:06:36,120
I've always supported you.

89
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:36,560
Yes.

90
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:37,870
Do you understand?

91
00:06:37,870 --> 00:06:38,630
Understood.

92
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:39,750
Um...

93
00:06:39,870 --> 00:06:41,400
That foreign exchange deal

94
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:43,430
is guaranteed to be completed
before the Spring Festival.

95
00:06:43,430 --> 00:06:44,120
Okay.

96
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:44,950
Mr. Ma,

97
00:06:45,190 --> 00:06:47,070
here's your flower basket.
Please sign for it.

98
00:06:47,070 --> 00:06:47,800
Give it to me.

99
00:06:54,430 --> 00:06:56,310
Ma Derong, you deserve to die!

100
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:57,930
What's going on?

101
00:06:58,120 --> 00:07:00,310
Probably some holdout
from the demolition village.

102
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:01,330
I'll explain to you inside.

103
00:07:01,330 --> 00:07:02,310
Quick, please.

104
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,390
You killed my whole family!

105
00:07:04,390 --> 00:07:05,510
You deserve to die!

106
00:07:05,510 --> 00:07:06,630
I'm going to kill you!

107
00:07:06,630 --> 00:07:08,070
I'll kill you!

108
00:07:27,950 --> 00:07:29,510
What on earth are you doing?

109
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:32,220
Can't you stop being so reckless?

110
00:07:33,790 --> 00:07:35,990
Ma Derong has been rooted
in Nanping for decades.

111
00:07:35,990 --> 00:07:38,630
Your actions will put us all
in a difficult position.

112
00:07:38,630 --> 00:07:40,030
With your own abilities,

113
00:07:40,070 --> 00:07:42,670
your materials
will just sink without a trace.

114
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,440
If you don't trust me,

115
00:07:44,590 --> 00:07:46,390
let's just pretend we never met.

116
00:07:50,770 --> 00:07:53,640
Who do you plan to give the materials to?

117
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,250
That's my business.

118
00:07:56,070 --> 00:07:57,680
You just need to give the materials to me.

119
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:58,600
You can't handle this,

120
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,390
but I can.

121
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:06,920
I've been by Ma Derong's side
for so many years.

122
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,930
I know how to get around his connections

123
00:08:08,930 --> 00:08:10,190
and avoid his network.

124
00:08:19,270 --> 00:08:21,070
Xia Xue is still in his hands.

125
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:25,070
This is your last chance.

126
00:08:29,190 --> 00:08:30,450
Why are you helping me?

127
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:32,880
I'm not helping you.

128
00:08:34,789 --> 00:08:35,919
I'm helping Xia Xue.

129
00:08:42,260 --> 00:08:44,120
But let me remind you of one thing.

130
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:47,000
If Ma Derong is really taken down one day,

131
00:08:47,130 --> 00:08:49,790
you'll cut off
a lot of people's income streams.

132
00:08:49,910 --> 00:08:51,480
Those people will tear you apart

133
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:52,410
like rabid dogs.

134
00:08:57,510 --> 00:08:59,240
Have you ever thought about it?

135
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:02,820
With your current abilities,

136
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,840
how can you protect Xia Xue?

137
00:09:11,590 --> 00:09:13,250
I'll wait for your materials.

138
00:10:28,510 --> 00:10:29,060
Mr. Ma,

139
00:10:29,510 --> 00:10:29,640
tomorrow's signing ceremony

140
00:10:29,640 --> 00:10:30,510
[On the Eve of the Signing Ceremony]

141
00:10:30,510 --> 00:10:32,200
will start promptly at 10:48.

142
00:10:32,660 --> 00:10:32,720
We've invited the city officials,

143
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:34,600
[Nanping Shipyard Production
Facility Project Signing Ceremony]

144
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:36,330
and the media will be there too.

145
00:10:36,750 --> 00:10:38,360
After the signing ceremony,

146
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:40,160
there's a champagne reception.

147
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:42,760
Do you want to go over the rundown

148
00:10:42,870 --> 00:10:43,670
with the host?

149
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:48,670
Mr. Ma,

150
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:51,080
there's trouble at the shipyard.

151
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:51,930
The provincial inspection team

152
00:10:51,930 --> 00:10:54,860
suddenly arrived at the shipyard
for an inspection.

153
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:29,720
Mr. Ma,

154
00:11:30,790 --> 00:11:32,320
I've done what you asked.

155
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:39,330
[Position: Clerk, Hengchuang Group]

156
00:11:39,330 --> 00:11:40,440
[Name: Li Jiayong]

157
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:40,980
Mr. Ma,

158
00:11:41,630 --> 00:11:42,750
Lu Ming gathered a group of villagers,

159
00:11:42,750 --> 00:11:45,200
wrote material
smearing you and the shipyard.

160
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,570
They managed to slip past our watch

161
00:11:46,570 --> 00:11:46,750
[Name: Li Fugui]

162
00:11:46,750 --> 00:11:48,970
and submitted the evidence
directly to the court.

163
00:11:48,970 --> 00:11:51,600
It was too late for our men
to intercept them.

164
00:11:51,630 --> 00:11:53,870
The authorities sent a team
for a surprise inspection

165
00:11:53,870 --> 00:11:55,600
all because of what they did.

166
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:00,540
Don't let a single person

167
00:12:00,540 --> 00:12:01,740
on that list get away.

168
00:12:02,470 --> 00:12:03,530
Including Lu Ming.

169
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:04,290
Yes, sir.

170
00:12:27,670 --> 00:12:29,970
Please don't smash it!

171
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,020
Please don't!

172
00:12:32,300 --> 00:12:33,960
I'm begging you, please stop!

173
00:13:09,800 --> 00:13:11,960
You seem pretty tough.

174
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:16,000
Why do you have to

175
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,030
offend Mr. Ma?

176
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:18,930
Do you have a death wish?

177
00:13:20,790 --> 00:13:23,250
I've prepared a lot of bottles
for you today.

178
00:13:25,550 --> 00:13:26,320
Let's see

179
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:28,690
how many hits you can take.

180
00:13:42,790 --> 00:13:43,680
Let him go!

181
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:46,150
You hear me? Let go!

182
00:13:46,170 --> 00:13:47,150
Stop it!

183
00:13:48,870 --> 00:13:49,930
What are you doing?

184
00:13:50,550 --> 00:13:51,110
Stop!

185
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:51,750
What?

186
00:13:52,630 --> 00:13:53,910
What's going on?

187
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:54,930
Nobody move!

188
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:05,030
Uncle San.

189
00:14:15,980 --> 00:14:17,270
That was ruthless.

190
00:14:20,670 --> 00:14:21,310
Chang.

191
00:14:23,280 --> 00:14:24,130
Take him away.

192
00:14:30,340 --> 00:14:31,100
Uncle San.

193
00:14:35,460 --> 00:14:36,750
You can protect him for now,

194
00:14:36,750 --> 00:14:38,680
but you can't protect him forever.

195
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:39,750
Don't forget,

196
00:14:39,980 --> 00:14:41,940
he offended Ma Derong.

197
00:14:55,440 --> 00:14:56,540
What are you doing?

198
00:14:57,910 --> 00:14:58,910
Alright.

199
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:07,120
Back off.

200
00:15:07,120 --> 00:15:08,250
Everyone, back off.

201
00:15:08,490 --> 00:15:09,220
Back off.

202
00:15:16,450 --> 00:15:17,510
I've offended you.

203
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:19,740
Not at all.

204
00:15:24,270 --> 00:15:25,270
Uncle San!

205
00:15:26,150 --> 00:15:27,790
Take care!

206
00:15:37,590 --> 00:15:38,230
Let's go.

207
00:15:38,840 --> 00:15:40,100
Mr. Ma wants to see you.

208
00:16:19,110 --> 00:16:20,510
How have you been lately?

209
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:22,850
I've been a bit busy,

210
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:24,800
so I haven't had time for you.

211
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:30,830
This house should be safe for now.

212
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:33,050
If you're used to living here,

213
00:16:33,050 --> 00:16:33,810
you can stay.

214
00:16:36,030 --> 00:16:37,090
If you want to move,

215
00:16:37,390 --> 00:16:38,720
I can't stop you either.

216
00:16:40,390 --> 00:16:41,720
But time is running out.

217
00:16:42,670 --> 00:16:43,730
Don't mess around.

218
00:16:48,720 --> 00:16:50,780
I really underestimated you people.

219
00:16:53,750 --> 00:16:55,480
The police should be here soon.

220
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:57,050
What do you mean?

221
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:02,480
Those whistleblowing materials,

222
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:03,910
didn't you submit them?

223
00:17:08,790 --> 00:17:10,000
Stop acting.

224
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:19,530
It doesn't matter anymore.

225
00:17:20,339 --> 00:17:22,200
Take good care of the child for me.

226
00:17:22,440 --> 00:17:23,160
Please.

227
00:17:24,069 --> 00:17:25,680
How I take care of this child

228
00:17:27,160 --> 00:17:28,560
is none of your business.

229
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:40,310
That is a Ma family child.

230
00:17:40,310 --> 00:17:41,960
It's none of my business?

231
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:43,200
None of my business?

232
00:17:48,310 --> 00:17:49,570
None of my business...

233
00:17:55,240 --> 00:17:57,200
If I ever find out you didn't
give birth to the child,

234
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:59,640
or that you treat her badly
after she's born,

235
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:01,070
even if I'm in prison,

236
00:18:02,960 --> 00:18:04,020
I won't let you off.

237
00:18:04,660 --> 00:18:05,510
Mark my words!

238
00:18:10,400 --> 00:18:11,160
Xia Xue,

239
00:18:13,290 --> 00:18:14,480
I don't ask for your forgiveness.

240
00:18:14,480 --> 00:18:15,590
This is just a deal.

241
00:18:16,310 --> 00:18:17,590
I have the DV.

242
00:18:26,070 --> 00:18:27,330
Look out for yourself.

243
00:18:54,690 --> 00:18:57,720
[Police]

244
00:19:04,410 --> 00:19:05,400
[Ambition Spanning Spring and Autumn]

245
00:19:05,400 --> 00:19:06,400
Thank you, man.

246
00:19:12,110 --> 00:19:14,910
Before Ma Derong was arrested,
he put out the word:

247
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:16,110
he must find you.

248
00:19:16,640 --> 00:19:18,300
You should go hide for a while.

249
00:19:18,350 --> 00:19:19,150
I can't hide.

250
00:19:20,440 --> 00:19:21,700
You offended Ma Derong

251
00:19:21,790 --> 00:19:22,720
to save me.

252
00:19:24,030 --> 00:19:25,000
I need to settle this.

253
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:26,730
It's not as simple as you think.

254
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:29,080
Ma Derong may be down now,

255
00:19:29,720 --> 00:19:31,070
but there are countless people
like Zhao Dabao

256
00:19:31,070 --> 00:19:33,790
who relied on Ma Derong for a living.

257
00:19:34,440 --> 00:19:35,640
You destroyed their livelihood,

258
00:19:35,640 --> 00:19:37,700
so they're bound to take it out on you.

259
00:19:37,830 --> 00:19:39,360
I'm not trying to scare you,

260
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:41,480
but you're in huge danger right now.

261
00:19:41,590 --> 00:19:42,750
You need to go lie low for a while.

262
00:19:42,750 --> 00:19:44,880
I've already arranged a place for you.

263
00:19:45,200 --> 00:19:47,160
Once things calm down here,

264
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,160
you can come back.

265
00:19:48,720 --> 00:19:49,400
Uncle San,

266
00:19:51,200 --> 00:19:52,730
this started because of me.

267
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:55,800
I can't leave.

268
00:19:57,790 --> 00:20:00,640
Ming, are you still thinking
about that woman?

269
00:20:04,640 --> 00:20:06,270
Wake up.

270
00:20:06,270 --> 00:20:08,160
You can barely protect

271
00:20:08,160 --> 00:20:09,640
yourself now.

272
00:20:09,640 --> 00:20:10,680
What's the point of thinking about her?

273
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:13,080
You might end up
dragging her into this too!

274
00:20:14,110 --> 00:20:14,790
Yesterday,

275
00:20:15,110 --> 00:20:16,070
if I hadn't brought my men

276
00:20:16,070 --> 00:20:17,970
to save you from Zhao Dabao,

277
00:20:18,160 --> 00:20:18,680
just think about

278
00:20:18,680 --> 00:20:20,270
what would have happened to you!

279
00:20:20,270 --> 00:20:21,330
Do you understand?

280
00:20:24,550 --> 00:20:25,440
I understand.

281
00:20:31,030 --> 00:20:32,160
You chose this path,

282
00:20:33,590 --> 00:20:36,390
so you have to grit your teeth
and walk it to the end.

283
00:20:52,200 --> 00:20:52,880
Xia Xue,

284
00:20:53,920 --> 00:20:54,850
you're free now.

285
00:21:00,240 --> 00:21:02,440
Lu Ming is waiting for you at Huxin Park.

286
00:21:02,550 --> 00:21:03,310
Go on.

287
00:21:11,030 --> 00:21:11,750
Go.

288
00:22:34,440 --> 00:22:37,490
♪ Let this farewell ♪

289
00:22:39,640 --> 00:22:42,840
♪ Freeze one thought ♪

290
00:22:44,390 --> 00:22:47,090
♪ In a fleeting instant ♪

291
00:22:49,670 --> 00:22:52,490
♪ The vacuum spreads ♪

292
00:22:54,960 --> 00:22:59,310
♪ Before the mist fades away ♪

293
00:23:02,850 --> 00:23:05,370
♪ A passing wind ♪

294
00:23:07,120 --> 00:23:11,500
♪ Reminds me to say goodbye ♪

295
00:23:12,990 --> 00:23:15,210
♪ Leave a single tear ♪

296
00:23:17,350 --> 00:23:21,350
♪ For time to tend ♪

297
00:23:23,430 --> 00:23:25,640
♪ Those lives that crossed ours ♪

298
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:32,460
♪ Do you still remember ♪

299
00:23:35,100 --> 00:23:39,830
♪ Everything from before ♪

300
00:23:46,420 --> 00:23:47,080
Yesterday,

301
00:23:47,410 --> 00:23:48,350
if I hadn't brought my men

302
00:23:48,350 --> 00:23:50,270
to save you from Zhao Dabao,

303
00:23:50,570 --> 00:23:51,030
just think about

304
00:23:51,030 --> 00:23:52,720
what would have happened to you!

305
00:23:52,720 --> 00:23:53,780
Do you understand?

306
00:24:00,340 --> 00:24:02,070
Have you ever thought about it?

307
00:24:02,440 --> 00:24:04,100
With your current abilities,

308
00:24:04,880 --> 00:24:06,510
how can you protect Xia Xue?

309
00:24:07,480 --> 00:24:09,780
♪ A passing wind ♪

310
00:24:11,400 --> 00:24:15,860
♪ Reminds me to say goodbye ♪

311
00:24:17,300 --> 00:24:19,830
♪ Leave a single tear ♪

312
00:24:21,560 --> 00:24:25,790
♪ For time to tend ♪

313
00:24:28,140 --> 00:24:30,200
♪ Those lives that crossed ours ♪

314
00:24:31,180 --> 00:24:37,000
♪ Do you still remember ♪

315
00:24:40,260 --> 00:24:45,990
♪ Everything from before ♪

316
00:24:50,270 --> 00:24:56,320
♪ Everything from before ♪

317
00:25:22,270 --> 00:25:23,670
Why won't you see Xia Xue?

318
00:25:27,280 --> 00:25:29,880
Do you know how long
she's been looking for you?

319
00:25:33,520 --> 00:25:34,520
It's safer for her

320
00:25:36,590 --> 00:25:37,590
if I don't see her.

321
00:25:40,590 --> 00:25:41,520
What do you mean?

322
00:25:42,920 --> 00:25:44,750
Wasn't Ma Derong arrested?

323
00:25:46,960 --> 00:25:48,590
Ma Derong is in prison,

324
00:25:49,590 --> 00:25:51,520
but we don't know the sentence yet.

325
00:25:52,350 --> 00:25:54,270
It definitely won't be the death penalty.

326
00:25:54,270 --> 00:25:56,240
All those people
who relied on him for a living,

327
00:25:56,240 --> 00:25:58,010
they're out of work now because of me.

328
00:25:58,010 --> 00:26:00,670
They will surely find ways
to take revenge on me.

329
00:26:04,330 --> 00:26:06,160
I thought it was all over.

330
00:26:07,310 --> 00:26:09,040
I rented a place on Huli Road.

331
00:26:11,160 --> 00:26:11,960
And this card.

332
00:26:12,730 --> 00:26:14,930
I'll deposit money into it every month.

333
00:26:19,310 --> 00:26:21,040
Please give it to Xia Xue for me.

334
00:26:22,980 --> 00:26:24,310
Give it to her yourself.

335
00:26:27,080 --> 00:26:27,880
Lin Hua,

336
00:26:30,160 --> 00:26:31,420
I've accepted my fate.

337
00:26:46,030 --> 00:26:47,400
Let's just live on.

338
00:27:14,310 --> 00:27:15,110
Ming,

339
00:27:16,590 --> 00:27:17,590
we've settled

340
00:27:18,160 --> 00:27:19,510
our debts last time.

341
00:27:19,930 --> 00:27:21,330
I forgot to give you this.

342
00:27:24,830 --> 00:27:25,750
You keep it.

343
00:27:27,510 --> 00:27:28,640
I still owe you a lot.

344
00:27:28,960 --> 00:27:29,550
Why?

345
00:27:30,240 --> 00:27:31,840
You still want to work for me?

346
00:27:32,000 --> 00:27:32,640
Yeah.

347
00:27:36,660 --> 00:27:38,120
You can't do that anymore.

348
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:41,880
Why?

349
00:27:42,750 --> 00:27:43,590
I want

350
00:27:46,110 --> 00:27:47,880
my men to follow you from now on.

351
00:27:52,030 --> 00:27:52,880
Me?

352
00:27:53,030 --> 00:27:54,110
I'm getting old.

353
00:27:54,960 --> 00:27:56,960
I'm handing the company over to you.

354
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:59,860
No matter how much money you make,

355
00:28:01,240 --> 00:28:03,590
just make sure they can make a living.

356
00:28:05,640 --> 00:28:07,440
I have the least seniority here.

357
00:28:07,590 --> 00:28:10,190
Even Chang has been with you
longer than I have.

358
00:28:10,240 --> 00:28:12,380
I can't do it.

359
00:28:14,270 --> 00:28:16,400
You've been with me the shortest time.

360
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:18,880
Do you know why I chose you?

361
00:28:21,510 --> 00:28:22,350
You're young

362
00:28:23,640 --> 00:28:24,830
and educated,

363
00:28:25,790 --> 00:28:27,390
with good vision and brains.

364
00:28:28,030 --> 00:28:30,430
They certainly won't have any objections.

365
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:38,510
In accordance with the Criminal Law
of the People's Republic of China's

366
00:28:38,510 --> 00:28:40,030
Article 234,

367
00:28:40,030 --> 00:28:41,680
Article 274,

368
00:28:41,680 --> 00:28:43,060
and Article 290,

369
00:28:43,080 --> 00:28:44,310
defendant Ma Derong

370
00:28:44,310 --> 00:28:45,830
is guilty of intentional injury,

371
00:28:45,830 --> 00:28:47,160
extortion,

372
00:28:47,160 --> 00:28:49,040
and gathering a crowd
to disturb social order.

373
00:28:49,040 --> 00:28:50,350
Punished for combined crimes,

374
00:28:50,350 --> 00:28:53,920
Ma Derong is sentenced
to ten years in prison.

375
00:29:01,510 --> 00:29:04,670
In the high-profile Ma Derong case,

376
00:29:04,750 --> 00:29:06,440
individuals connected to the case

377
00:29:06,440 --> 00:29:09,390
suspected of violations
of law and discipline

378
00:29:09,410 --> 00:29:11,270
have, according to the severity
of their circumstances,

379
00:29:11,270 --> 00:29:14,330
been lawfully sentenced
to corresponding penalties.

380
00:29:17,820 --> 00:29:20,920
[Several Months Later]

381
00:29:21,680 --> 00:29:23,400
Don't cry.

382
00:29:40,510 --> 00:29:43,960
This next song is for Mr. Ming!

383
00:30:00,640 --> 00:30:01,960
Alright.

384
00:30:01,960 --> 00:30:03,050
It's okay, baby.

385
00:30:22,750 --> 00:30:23,490
Come here.

386
00:30:23,550 --> 00:30:24,310
Be careful.

387
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:27,070
Take it slow.

388
00:30:31,110 --> 00:30:31,910
Get in the car.

389
00:30:37,920 --> 00:30:39,640
Thanks for coming so late.

390
00:30:40,350 --> 00:30:41,400
Don't mention it.

391
00:31:18,350 --> 00:31:19,070
Xia Xue,

392
00:31:19,680 --> 00:31:22,340
forgive me for leaving
without saying goodbye.

393
00:31:23,350 --> 00:31:26,270
Forgive me for being unable
to keep our promise.

394
00:31:28,590 --> 00:31:30,200
Forgive me for giving my all,

395
00:31:31,340 --> 00:31:33,640
yet only to watch you walk away.

396
00:31:36,070 --> 00:31:37,030
My life

397
00:31:37,640 --> 00:31:39,090
no longer belongs to me.

398
00:31:41,240 --> 00:31:43,200
But I hope in the future, you will

399
00:31:44,070 --> 00:31:45,550
walk out of the darkness

400
00:31:46,830 --> 00:31:48,420
and into the light.

401
00:32:09,730 --> 00:32:12,640
[2010]

402
00:32:33,960 --> 00:32:35,620
The police came to see you too?

403
00:32:37,680 --> 00:32:39,540
I didn't tell the police anything

404
00:32:40,270 --> 00:32:42,070
about the child's background.

405
00:32:44,240 --> 00:32:46,300
I'll keep looking for Shanshan, too.

406
00:32:58,000 --> 00:33:01,700
[Missing on June 5]
[Hou Jun, Stepfather] [Xia Xue]

407
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:06,310
[Hou Shanshan]

408
00:33:06,310 --> 00:33:07,600
[Biological Father]

409
00:33:10,300 --> 00:33:12,660
[Hou Jun, Husband & Wife, Xia Xue]

410
00:33:15,300 --> 00:33:18,340
[Lu Ming, Childhood Friends, Xia Xue]

411
00:33:20,960 --> 00:33:21,510
Ren Yi,

412
00:33:22,050 --> 00:33:22,750
find out

413
00:33:22,750 --> 00:33:24,440
which hospital Xia Xue
gave birth to Hou Shanshan at.

414
00:33:24,440 --> 00:33:25,160
Pull up the prenatal checkup

415
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:26,240
records for me.

416
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:32,500
Nanping Bo'ai International Hospital.

417
00:33:33,920 --> 00:33:36,180
Nanping Bo'ai International Hospital?

418
00:33:36,200 --> 00:33:36,720
Wen,

419
00:33:36,720 --> 00:33:38,310
is there a problem with this hospital?

420
00:33:38,310 --> 00:33:39,970
Not with the hospital itself.

421
00:33:40,590 --> 00:33:41,830
But this is the most expensive

422
00:33:41,830 --> 00:33:43,030
hospital in Nanping.

423
00:33:43,200 --> 00:33:46,370
When Xia Xue
give birth to Hou Shanshan at 21,

424
00:33:47,310 --> 00:33:49,640
she shouldn't have been able to afford it.

425
00:33:50,960 --> 00:33:53,560
So, Hou Shanshan's
biological father is rich.

426
00:33:58,250 --> 00:34:03,380
[Hou Shanshan]
[Biological Father]

427
00:34:03,430 --> 00:34:03,790
[Nanping Bo'ai International Hospital
Obstetrics Office]

428
00:34:03,790 --> 00:34:04,550
Officers,

429
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:07,110
it's not that I don't want to cooperate.

430
00:34:07,110 --> 00:34:09,190
But regarding the files
from ten years ago,

431
00:34:09,190 --> 00:34:11,570
the records weren't digitized.

432
00:34:11,840 --> 00:34:12,360
Our hospital

433
00:34:12,360 --> 00:34:13,920
simply didn't have the capacity

434
00:34:13,920 --> 00:34:15,030
to preserve them.

435
00:34:15,230 --> 00:34:17,360
So we really can't provide

436
00:34:17,710 --> 00:34:19,510
the maternity records you want.

437
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:22,239
I understand.

438
00:34:23,070 --> 00:34:24,800
Since there are no patient records,

439
00:34:24,800 --> 00:34:27,070
do you have
the personnel records from that time?

440
00:34:27,070 --> 00:34:27,800
Those we have.

441
00:34:27,800 --> 00:34:28,800
Just a moment.

442
00:34:28,880 --> 00:34:29,480
Thank you.

443
00:34:37,630 --> 00:34:38,760
Here, take a look.

444
00:34:41,739 --> 00:34:43,780
[Employee Personnel Registration Form]

445
00:34:44,070 --> 00:34:45,590
I'd like to ask you something.

446
00:34:45,590 --> 00:34:47,449
Among the obstetricians back then,

447
00:34:47,449 --> 00:34:48,780
who was the most famous?

448
00:34:48,960 --> 00:34:50,290
The hardest one to book.

449
00:34:50,670 --> 00:34:51,600
Do you remember?

450
00:34:51,840 --> 00:34:52,710
Of course I do.

451
00:34:52,920 --> 00:34:54,110
It would definitely be Dr. Xu.

452
00:34:54,110 --> 00:34:54,550
Now,

453
00:34:54,550 --> 00:34:55,679
she is President Xu.

454
00:34:55,679 --> 00:34:56,070
[Specialty: Clinical Medicine]
[Department: Obstetrics & Gynecology]

455
00:34:56,070 --> 00:34:57,920
Could you give us her contact info?

456
00:34:57,920 --> 00:34:59,070
Sure, I'll write it down for you.

457
00:34:59,070 --> 00:34:59,450
Okay.

458
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:03,320
Here.

459
00:35:03,900 --> 00:35:04,630
[President Xu's phone number]

460
00:35:04,630 --> 00:35:05,400
Thank you.

461
00:35:16,550 --> 00:35:17,480
Officers,

462
00:35:17,480 --> 00:35:18,630
you may not know

463
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:21,150
how many pregnant women
I treat every year.

464
00:35:21,150 --> 00:35:22,480
It's been so many years.

465
00:35:23,840 --> 00:35:25,240
I really can't remember.

466
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:32,800
President Xu,

467
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:34,960
we just said

468
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:37,030
we wanted to ask about
this pregnant woman,

469
00:35:37,030 --> 00:35:39,280
but we didn't say which year it was.

470
00:35:42,150 --> 00:35:44,550
Why did you assume it's been many years?

471
00:35:49,840 --> 00:35:50,640
President Xu,

472
00:35:50,790 --> 00:35:52,070
regarding the questions we ask,

473
00:35:52,070 --> 00:35:53,760
whether you tell us voluntarily

474
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:55,090
or we find out ourselves

475
00:35:55,150 --> 00:35:56,480
makes a big difference.

476
00:36:07,230 --> 00:36:08,550
Her name is Xia Xue.

477
00:36:09,920 --> 00:36:10,880
Ten years ago,

478
00:36:11,400 --> 00:36:12,880
she was a patient of mine.

479
00:36:14,800 --> 00:36:16,730
It's fine. The fever has gone down.

480
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:21,620
Do you remember the name of
the family member who accompanied her?

481
00:36:23,280 --> 00:36:23,960
Thank you.

482
00:36:24,110 --> 00:36:25,710
Call me if you need anything.

483
00:36:33,920 --> 00:36:34,980
His name is Hou Jun.

484
00:36:40,320 --> 00:36:40,920
How is it?

485
00:36:41,380 --> 00:36:42,510
What did the doctor say?

486
00:36:42,510 --> 00:36:43,550
She's fine now.

487
00:36:44,800 --> 00:36:45,730
That's a relief.

488
00:36:46,760 --> 00:36:48,550
I'm sorry to trouble you.

489
00:36:50,070 --> 00:36:52,130
You don't need to be so polite with me.

490
00:36:52,190 --> 00:36:53,590
It's the least I could do.

491
00:36:55,230 --> 00:36:56,230
You should go back and rest.

492
00:36:56,230 --> 00:36:57,630
It's been a whole night.

493
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:00,550
Look at you now,

494
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:03,490
raising a child on your own.

495
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:05,860
This isn't a long-term solution.

496
00:37:11,510 --> 00:37:12,510
Anyway, I'm here.

497
00:37:13,420 --> 00:37:14,320
If anything happens,

498
00:37:14,320 --> 00:37:15,880
just call me anytime.

499
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:19,760
Not feeling well?

500
00:37:19,760 --> 00:37:21,230
I know you're not feeling well.

501
00:37:21,230 --> 00:37:22,000
Be good.

502
00:37:23,550 --> 00:37:25,840
Shall I sing you a song?

503
00:37:26,000 --> 00:37:28,190
Little swallow,

504
00:37:29,190 --> 00:37:31,630
wearing floral clothes,

505
00:37:32,110 --> 00:37:36,960
comes here every spring.

506
00:37:37,760 --> 00:37:42,550
I ask the swallow why you come,

507
00:37:43,150 --> 00:37:45,400
the swallow says...
